    "The results are shown in Table 7.",
    "The statements of four students in the focus group interview pointed out that Metaverse-powered online flipped learning increased the student-student interaction while three participants stated that it did not affect the student-student interaction.",
    "On the other hand, two of them claimed that it restricted student-student interaction whereas one participant reported that it restricted teacher-student interaction: P12: My interaction increased thanks to assignments.",
    "P6: It did not affect my interaction with my friends.",
    "P1: So I think it limits social interaction between students."
